body:
#### PR description:
There is issue #37906, massive LogWarnings from GEM DQM. It was due to the incomplete part of GE21/GE0. As progress on the development for GE21/GE0 DQM, the part has been updated and there are no more such LogWarnings.

#### PR validation:
Test are done and one can check again by `runTheMatrix` workflows

@jshlee @watson-ij
title: [GEM] add DQM plots for GE21/GE0 and Fix on massive LogWarnings
